summary: You express a aurelian precision: vision shaped by choreographer discipline.

lore.long: You move through learning like a ritual: observe, practice, iterate. When balanced, your skill compounds. When depleted, you can become harsh with yourself—your edge is gentleness that still keeps standards.

name: The Vesper Restorer of Silent Symposium

summary: You express a vesper precision: vision shaped by restorer discipline.
